- **Project Overview**
  - This is a Search&Filter monorepo containing a Cursor multi-agent workflow system for Figma design audits and a React/TypeScript prototype application
  - Root package.json defines workspace-level scripts for Figma sync operations
  - Main application code lives in `prototype/` directory

- **Root Directory Structure**
  ```
  Search&Filter/
  ├── .cursor/rules/          # Cursor rule definitions
  ├── agents/                  # Multi-agent workflow definitions
  ├── guides/                  # Setup and usage guides
  ├── prompts/                 # Style guide and prompts
  ├── prototype/               # React/TypeScript application
  ├── reports/                 # Generated reports and templates
  ├── rules/                   # JSON rule configurations
  ├── scripts/                 # Utility scripts
  ├── package.json            # Root workspace config
  └── README.md               # Project documentation
  ```

